author: Disney
description:
Discover how Walt Disney Imagineering and Pixar collaborated to bring the Parr House, inspired by Disney and Pixar’s “Incredibles 2,” to life at Cotino, the first Storyliving by Disney community located in Rancho Mirage, California. 

This first-of-its-kind project for Walt Disney Imagineering took an idea from big screen to real world like never before.  

For more information about the Cotino community, visit Cotino.com.
